As somehow the Ark was powering down (God knows how) Teletran 1 warned Maxima 
again. 

Maxima transformed into her bot mode & landed on the hill summit across from 
the Ark.

&quot;LEAVE THIS AREA NOW, AUTOBOTS! IF YOU VALUE YOUR LIVES!&quot; she boomed with 
great anger in her voice. 

Her form was different from last she &#39;met&#39; these bots, now a mix of a white 
tiger & a hawk, a sort of TM mix with a tad BM, she shimmered in the sunlight. 
The metallic wings flexed & spread out to intimidate the Bots.

Her crimson optics glowed as she growled at the Autobots below. then focused 
upon Empath. 

&quot;EMPATH! I FIND IT MORE THAN WISE THAT YOU LEAVE TELETRAN 1 ALONE & STOP 
MESSING AROUND WITH THE ARK&#39;S POWER! NOW!&quot; She growled. &quot;LEST YOU WANT THOSE IN 
THE BRIDGE TO BE IN DANGER!&quot; 

Her main concern was for Megatron.. of course. But she felt she had a duty, & 
more to protect all of them. It didn&#39;t matter about the Autobots what they 
felt or Scourge. Actually, she didn&#39;t trust anyone. Except one bot. 

She glanced behind her as the others approached. 

&quot;LEAVE NOW! I PREPARE FOR BATTLE!&quot;

